{"title":"All","description":"\u003ch2\u003eSweeten your day with our delicious treats\u003c\/h2\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"motichur-laddu","title":"Motichoor Laddu","description":"\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"pro-des-title pro-info-box\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eIndia's Favourite Laddu\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience the authentic taste of Dadu's Signature Motichoor Laddu, meticulously crafted with premium ingredients and time-honoured techniques. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRenowned for its unmatched consistency in taste, texture, and form, this laddu is so soft it melts in your mouth with a gentle touch. It's no wonder that this sweet delight is one of the best sellers in India. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulge in the ultimate treat that embodies the rich tradition and exceptional quality Dadu's is known for.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMotichoor Laddu is a cherished delicacy with ancient roots in Hindu culture, especially popular during cultural \u0026amp; festive seasons, Dussehra, and Diwali, embodying the essence of Indian tradition.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003ca style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\" title=\"Watch how Dadu's Motichoor Laddu gets made\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/reel\/Chq9WTcBscZ\/?igsh=eTR1Yzk2ZDF6NmRo\"\u003eWATCH\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e the craftsmanship in action\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eKey Features\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003ePremium Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/h4\u003e\