n of chickpea flour, sugar, ghee (clarified butter), and various nuts like almonds and pistachios.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"pro-description-box pro-info-box\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eShelf Life\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e30 days from packaging\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eIngredients\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKhova Gujia - \u003c\/strong\u003e Maida, Besan, Ghee, Sugar, Badam, Pista \u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMtichoor Laddu - \u003c\/strong\u003eMaida, Besan, Ghee, Sugar\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKaju Katli - \u003c\/strong\u003e Cashew, milk, Ghee,Sugar\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAjmeeri Kalakand - \u003c\/strong\u003e Cashew, milk, Ghee, Sugar\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Mysore Pak - \u003c\/strong\u003eCashew, milk, Ghee, Sugar\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuryakala -\u003c\/strong\u003e Wheat, Almond, Cashew, milk, Ghee, Sugar\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eStorage Instructions\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore in a cool and dry place\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":44745148006680,"sku":null,"price":315.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","offer_id":44745147973912,"sku":"501","price":630.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Sohanpapdi_b58b2368-930e-46c2-8edf-43b17e0908d1.png?v=1771686408"},{"product_id":"ajwain-cookies","title":"Ajwain Cookies","description":"","brand":"D’PanCo (Baked Snacks and Confectionery)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45336442044696,"sku":null,"price":230.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","of