"Dryfruit Putharekulu","description":"\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eWith Love From Andhra\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExperience the unique and exquisite taste of Dadu’s Dry fruit Pootharekulu, a beloved sweet from Andhra Pradesh. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEach piece is wrapped in a wafer-thin rice starch layer that resembles paper, stuffed generously with sugar, dry fruits, and nuts. This traditional treat, known for its delicate texture and rich filling, is perfect for festivals, religious occasions, and weddings. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCelebrate the timeless charm of Dadu's Putharekulu, a sweet that brings joy to every moment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAt Dadu's, we ensure that you can shop your favourite sweets online with ease.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDadu's Dry Fruit Pootharekulu is delivered to your home with utmost care by our reliable logistics partners.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor international shipping inquiries, contact our support. Our clients within Hyderabad, India can get instant delivery using \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003ca style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\" href=\"https:\/\/www.swiggy.com\/menu\/2085?source=sharing\"\u003eSwiggy\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e or \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003ca style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\" href=\"https:\/\/zomato.onelink.me\/xqzv\/h1s29802\"\u003eZomato\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor a free tasting and a true gourmet experience, visit Dadu’s near you\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cb id=\"docs-int